text: Take one sample from fourth slot and measure the CV.
Take one sample from fifth slot and measure OCP and CV.
Take both samples again and measure CA for one hour in -0.2, -0.4 and -0.6 V.
Take one sample from fifth slot and measure CA, changing potential every 60 seconds by +100 mV from -1 to 0 V.
First measure OCP for 200 s, then CV (50 cycles from -0.2 to 0.2 V vs OCP), then CA for 1 h at -0.4 V vs OCP.
